FixtureType.Description: EclFresnel 2K is the LED replacement for a standard tungsten 2.000 W Fresnel. Featuring the output characteristics of a traditional Fresnel but with beam control, functional barn doors and a power source that focuses on outstanding colour rendition. The EclFresnel 2K adds all the advantages of LED to the Fresnel.
